cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting relevant motion events in home surveillance videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel network architecture, which could be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper addresses the problem of filtering out nuisance motion events, which could be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
